"""

HELP_TEXT = """Hello! I’m @monchhichiTCGbot 🧸✨

Buyer commands
/list — View your claimed items
/invoice — View your current unpaid invoice

Admin commands
/sell <name> | <price> | <quantity>
/adminsummary — View all claimants and unpaid totals
/markpaid <user_id> — Mark a user's current invoice as paid

Buyer action
Reply to sale post with: claim
